title: Victorious Graves skin
body: I got Gold before preseason in Ranked Solo/Duo and Ranked Flex, however I didn't still haven't received my Victorious Graves skin. I have received all the other rewards i.e. ward skin, summoner icons, and even the champion Graves (as I didn't previously own him) but I am still missing the skin. All of my friends have received it, it's just me that still doesn't have it.

replies.body:
Submit a support ticket and they'll be able to help you out.

https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new
